OL,10,FTwo people have been sentenced after
OL,11,Fpleading guilty to assisting a
OL,12,Fmurderer after he killed a teenager in
OL,13,FRadstock.
OL,15,FCharley Bates was stabbed by Joshua
OL,16,FDelbono at a car park in The Street on
OL,17,FSunday 31 July 2022.
