OL,3,CPair sentenced for helping murderer
OL,4,Chide knife and burn his clothes
OL,6,FDelbono received a life sentence in
OL,7,FApril 2023, and will serve a minimum
OL,8,Fof 21 years, after being found guilty
OL,9,Fof murder by a jury.
OL,11,FHowever, a man and a woman that helped
OL,12,Fhim in the aftermath of the murder
OL,13,Fhave been brought to justice too.
OL,15,FCCTV footage showed 20-year-old Jack
OL,16,FSeal travelling in a Citroen to the
OL,17,Fcar park in the centre of Radstock,
OL,18,Fwith Delbono travelling with his then-
OL,19,Fgirlfriend Lauren Ephgrave, 21, in the
OL,20,FSeat behind.
