OL,3,CPair sentenced for helping murderer
OL,4,Chide knife and burn his clothes
OL,6,FAfter Delbono had stabbed 16-year-old
OL,7,FCharley they fled the scene in the
OL,8,Fsame two vehicles, stopping at various
OL,9,Fpoints where they learned Charley had
OL,10,Fdied before heading to Shearwater
OL,11,FLake, near Warminster.
OL,13,FDuring his trial, Delbono admitted
OL,14,Fthat he threw the knife he used to
OL,15,Fmurder Charley into the lake. While at
OL,16,Fthe lake, Ephgrave took photos of
OL,17,Fclothes being burned in an attempt to
OL,18,Fdispose of evidence.
