OL,3,CPair sentenced for helping murderer
OL,4,Chide knife and burn his clothes
OL,6,FEphgrave, of Melksham, and Seal, of
OL,7,FFrome, both pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fassisting an offender and were
OL,9,Fsentenced by Judge William Hart at
OL,10,FBristol Crown Court today (Friday 1
OL,11,FMarch). A third person was charged
OL,12,Fwith the same offence and found not
OL,13,Fguilty in November last year.
OL,15,FEphgrave received a 10-month custodial
OL,16,Fsentence, suspended for 18 months, and
OL,17,Fmust engage in 20 days' rehabilitation
OL,18,Factivity.
