OL,3,CPair sentenced for helping murderer
OL,4,Chide knife and burn his clothes
OL,6,FSeal was sentenced to 15 months in
OL,7,Fprison, suspended for 18 months, and
OL,8,Fmust engage in 140 hours of unpaid
OL,9,Fwork within the next 12 months.
OL,11,FJudge Hart in sentencing the pair
OL,12,Fremarked both had chosen to help
OL,13,FDelbono after he fatally wounded
OL,14,FCharley, rather than the critically
OL,15,Finjured teenager. He also recognised
OL,16,Fthe dignity Charley's family had shown
OL,17,Fthroughout all the legal proceedings.
