OL,3,CPair sentenced for helping murderer
OL,4,Chide knife and burn his clothes
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Mark Newbury, of
OL,7,Fthe Major Crime Investigation Team,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Charley's tragic death caused a
OL,9,Fhuge amount of shock in Radstock. The
OL,10,Foutpouring of public grief that
OL,11,Ffollowed showed his popularity and how
OL,12,Fmuch he is missed by family and
OL,13,Ffriends.
OL,15,F"Today's hearing brings to a
OL,16,Fconclusion a significant police
OL,17,Finvestigation that has ensured that
OL,18,Fnot only a dangerous murderer is
OL,19,Fbehind bars, but now has seen two
OL,20,Fpeople who helped him on that fateful
OL,21,Fday receive criminal records too.
